    <item>
      <title>拉加德称经济“略弱于”预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-17/lagarde-says-economy-somewhat-weaker-than-expected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德在该央行年内第三次降息后的新闻发布会上表示，她预计欧元区经济将随着时间的推移而增强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-17/lagarde-says-economy-somewhat-weaker-than-expected</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 13:19:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罢工、飓风影响导致美国工业生产下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/us-industrial-production-declines-on-strike-hurricane-effects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[9月份美国工业生产出现下滑，部分原因是波音公司罢工和两场飓风导致工厂产量下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/us-industrial-production-declines-on-strike-hurricane-effects</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 13:18:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>气候目标在绿色和平总部遭遇不列颠哥伦比亚省选举反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/climate-goals-face-bc-election-backlash-in-home-of-greenpeace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大第三大省的一位意想不到的政治新贵，因对气候科学持怀疑态度而被其原先的政党开除，凭借着承诺放弃环境目标并大力开发自然资源，距离赢得政权仅一步之遥。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/climate-goals-face-bc-election-backlash-in-home-of-greenpeace</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 13:15:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国零售额增长超过预期，失业救济申请下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-17/us-retail-sales-rise-more-than-forecast-jobless-claims-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国 9 月份零售额增长幅度超过预期，整体呈上升趋势，而美国失业救济申请人数在截至 10 月 12 日的一周内意外下降 19,000 人至 241,000 人，而之前一周受飓风海伦影响的东南部各州失业救济申请人数出现激增。世界大型企业联合会首席经济学家 Dana Peterson 分析了这些数据。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-17/us-retail-sales-rise-more-than-forecast-jobless-claims-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 13:02:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行第三次降息以提振疲软的经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/ecb-cuts-rates-for-third-time-to-prop-up-weakening-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀加速回落，欧洲央行今年第三次下调利率，以支持该地区陷入困境的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/ecb-cuts-rates-for-third-time-to-prop-up-weakening-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 12:17:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织称波兰可能在 2025 年中期开始降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/imf-says-poland-may-start-gradual-interest-rate-cuts-in-mid-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，波兰可能在明年年中开始逐步降息，但建议央行行长在 2025 年全年保持紧缩货币政策，因为通胀风险很大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/imf-says-poland-may-start-gradual-interest-rate-cuts-in-mid-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 12:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典将修改预算规则以允许增加公共支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/sweden-to-change-budget-rules-to-allow-more-government-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典将放弃预算盈余目标，利用北欧国家的低债务水平来增加国防支出并恢复破旧的基础设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/sweden-to-change-budget-rules-to-allow-more-government-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 10:09:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因欧洲央行降息而扩大涨幅；雀巢股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/european-shares-little-changed-ahead-of-expected-ecb-rates-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受欧洲央行一如预期连续第二次降息以及科技股在连跌两日后企稳的影响，欧洲股市延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/european-shares-little-changed-ahead-of-expected-ecb-rates-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 07:12:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
